HEADWORD: Quinzaine
<hw>Quin"zaine</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F., from
<ets>quinze</ets> fifteen, L. <ets>quindecim</ets>. See
<er>Fifteen</er>.]</ety> <def>The fifteenth day after a feast day,
including both in the reckoning.</def> <altsp>[Written also
<asp>quinzain</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Quinze</ent>⟦br⟧
